Hi,

Following the suggestion from @abhioncbr about using [javax.ws.rs.NotAuthorizedException](https://docs.oracle.com/javaee/7/api/javax/ws/rs/NotAuthorizedException.html), this is the fix I currently use in my pinot broker : 

```java
if (httpHeaders.getHeaderString(HttpHeader.AUTHORIZATION) == null) {
   throw new NotAuthorizedException("Basic")
} else {
   throw new WebApplicationException("Permission Denied", Response.Status.FORBIDDEN)
}
```

